@tobegit3hub : Is it possible to provide a minimal reproducible example. As text instead of a screenshot so we can copy the exact code used ourselves?

With some more context we might be able to provide a useful diagnosis. The error log and snippet you've provided are just a little shy of being very useful. For example, it's not clear to me which line corresponds to task.py, line 120. And also, would be good to have the stacktrace of the InvalidArgumentException.

Do chime in with a small, reproducible example that we can run. Thanks!
